### POST login
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/v1/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "fish@stream.net",
  "password": "so-secure!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
%}
###

### GET configuration
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/v1/configuration

###

### PUT configuration (enabling everything)
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/v1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "enableForgetPassword": true,
  "enableRegistration": true,
  "enableReviewPendingRegistration": true
}
###

### PUT configuration (disabling everything)
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/v1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "enableForgetPassword": false,
  "enableRegistration": false,
  "enableReviewPendingRegistration": false
}
###

### PUT configuration (default)
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/v1/configuration
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "enableForgetPassword": false,
  "enableRegistration": true,
  "enableReviewPendingRegistration": true
}
